{"type":null,"faqId":49383,"title":"触屏操作","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.td1{width:2.2048612in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;}\n.td2{width:3.307639in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.r1{keep-together:always;}\n.t1{table-layout:fixed;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"触摸屏操作\"XE \"触屏手势\"</span>\n</p>\n<table class=\"t1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188921\" style=\"width:1.0513889in;height:1.2493056in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"触屏操作\"</span><span class=\"s1\">点击</span><span>：触碰目标一次。例如：点击以确认选择或打开应用程序。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188922\" style=\"width:1.0083333in;height:1.25in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">长按</span><span>：触碰目标并持续 2 秒以上。例如：长按主屏幕空白区域，可进入主屏幕编辑状态。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188923\" style=\"width:1.1180556in;height:1.2493056in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">滑动</span><span>：在屏幕上滑动手指。例如：在通知面板的“通知”页签下，左右滑动可关闭相应通知。在屏幕上快速地上下或左右滑动手指，可以滚动文档、前往其他主页或执行其他操作。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188924\" style=\"width:1.10625in;height:1.2493056in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">拖动</span><span>：长按目标，并将其移动到屏幕上的其他位置。例如：在主屏幕，拖动窗口小工具或图标到任意位置。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188925\" style=\"width:1.3423611in;height:1.25in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">两指分开</span><span>：在屏幕上分开两指。例如：在查看照片或浏览网页时，两指分开可对画面进行放大。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188926\" style=\"width:1.4583334in;height:1.0986111in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">两指合拢</span><span>：在屏幕上合拢两指。例如：在查看照片或浏览网页时，两指合拢可对画面进行缩小。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188927\" style=\"width:0.9340278in;height:1.25in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">三指合拢</span><span>：在主屏幕，三指合拢可打开主屏幕缩略图界面。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1090,"faqType":"开始使用","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5127","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Getting-know-phone","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294335000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":55,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}